"The course term is intentionally broad. DUL provides a foundational physical-object category, while SOMA provides robotics-oriented refinements for embodied activity contexts."@en owl:sameAs "The course term is intentionally broad. DUL provides a foundational physical-object category, while SOMA provides robotics-oriented refinements for embodied activity contexts."@en .

